[
  {
    "slide_index": 1,
    "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/slide_01.mp3",
    "duration": 33.888,
    "segments": [
      {
        "segment_index": 0,
        "text": "在这一页中，我们将探讨定义主要科技公司的核心部门。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_01_seg_0.mp3",
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 5.16,
        "duration": 5.16
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 1,
        "text": "这些部门包括广告变现、人工智能/机器学习平台、云基础设施和增长，这些都是推动收入和创新的重要因素。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_01_seg_1.mp3",
        "start": 5.16,
        "end": 15.864,
        "duration": 10.704
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 2,
        "text": "每个公司，比如谷歌、亚马逊、微软和苹果，都会根据其商业模式对这些部门给予不同的重视。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_01_seg_2.mp3",
        "start": 15.864,
        "end": 25.056,
        "duration": 9.192
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "例如，谷歌非常重视广告和人工智能，而亚马逊则将重心放在其AWS和市场上。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_01_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 25.056,
        "end": 33.84,
        "duration": 8.784
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "slide_index": 2,
    "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/slide_02.mp3",
    "duration": 37.584,
    "segments": [
      {
        "segment_index": 0,
        "text": "让我们深入探讨广告变现如何成为科技公司重要的收入驱动力。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_02_seg_0.mp3",
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 6.144,
        "duration": 6.144
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 1,
        "text": "专注于广告的部门至关重要，因为它们直接产生收入，尤其是对于像Google和Meta这样的公司。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_02_seg_1.mp3",
        "start": 6.144,
        "end": 14.688,
        "duration": 8.544
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 2,
        "text": "例如，Google Services的收入增长主要得益于搜索和YouTube广告，这两者每年就创造了超过600亿美元的收入。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_02_seg_2.mp3",
        "start": 14.688,
        "end": 24.24,
        "duration": 9.552
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "同样，亚马逊的广告业务也成为了与AWS并肩的重要利润来源，AWS在2026年第一季度报告的营业收入达到了142亿美元。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_02_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 24.24,
        "end": 37.536,
        "duration": 13.296
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "slide_index": 3,
    "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/slide_03.mp3",
    "duration": 31.176,
    "segments": [
      {
        "segment_index": 0,
        "text": "现在，让我们来探讨推荐算法在科技公司中的作用。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_03_seg_0.mp3",
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 5.4,
        "duration": 5.4
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 1,
        "text": "这些系统至关重要，因为它们决定了用户看到和互动的内容，直接影响用户参与度和收入。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_03_seg_1.mp3",
        "start": 5.4,
        "end": 13.584,
        "duration": 8.184
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 2,
        "text": "例如，TikTok的推荐系统是其用户体验的核心，而Netflix和Amazon也非常依赖个性化推荐来推动订阅和销售。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_03_seg_2.mp3",
        "start": 13.584,
        "end": 24.24,
        "duration": 10.656
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "这些算法的技术复杂性使它们成为这些公司中最具战略重要性的领域之一。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_03_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 24.24,
        "end": 31.128,
        "duration": 6.888
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "slide_index": 4,
    "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/slide_04.mp3",
    "duration": 29.064,
    "segments": [
      {
        "segment_index": 0,
        "text": "接下来，我们来讨论一下大型科技公司中的增长概念。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_04_seg_0.mp3",
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 5.304,
        "duration": 5.304
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 1,
        "text": "与传统营销不同，增长侧重于数据分析、实验和用户生命周期管理，以优化用户参与度。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_04_seg_1.mp3",
        "start": 5.304,
        "end": 14.088,
        "duration": 8.784
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 2,
        "text": "这包括用户获取、留存和转化的策略，这些对于长期成功至关重要。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_04_seg_2.mp3",
        "start": 14.088,
        "end": 20.808,
        "duration": 6.72
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "像Meta、TikTok和Amazon这样的公司都设立了专门的增长团队，专注于这些关键领域。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_04_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 20.808,
        "end": 29.016,
        "duration": 8.208
      }
    ]
  },
  {
