        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_05_seg_1.mp3",
        "start": 5.496,
        "end": 15.12,
        "duration": 9.624
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 2,
        "text": "例如，Google 的搜索和 YouTube、Amazon 的市场以及 Apple 的 iOS 对各自公司的成功至关重要。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_05_seg_2.mp3",
        "start": 15.12,
        "end": 23.712,
        "duration": 8.592
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "这些核心产品线通常会受到高层管理者的高度关注，因为它们直接影响公司的估值。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_05_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 23.712,
        "end": 31.656,
        "duration": 7.944
      }
    ]
  },
  {
