        "start": 16.44,
        "end": 26.016,
        "duration": 9.576
      },
      {
        "segment_index": 3,
        "text": "同样，Nvidia的数据中心收入达到了752亿美元，展示了对人工智能基础设施日益增长的需求。",
        "audio_path": "output_en_slide_cn_speaker/audio/segments/slide_06_seg_3.mp3",
        "start": 26.016,
        "end": 35.592,
        "duration": 9.576
      }
    ]
